{"tid":1183822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強國民眾瘋搶UNIQLO 網民：喪屍片現場","createTime":"2019-06-03T08:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T12:59:16.000Z","uid":75969,"like":227,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"c0fd2729d7f474fbb64d9313108750c10691d51a","tid":1183822,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:32:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Pi-IRFQBCBw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPi-IRFQBCBw&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOBvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=6fd0b61f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Pi-IRFQBCBw</a><br />\n<br />\n以招牌「XX眼」聞名的國際知名藝術家KAWS代表作「COMPANION」3月曾在維港海面展出，而KAWS與UNIQLO聯乘的「KAWS:SUMMER」UT系列今日則在中港台等地全線分店開賣。微博流傳內地UNIQLO的開賣情況，一眾粉絲爭先恐後衝入門店，網民形容如喪屍片現場。<br />\n<br />\n據網上多段流傳影片可見，有民眾在商場內往UNIQLO門店狂奔；也有片段顯示門店鐵閘才開了一條縫隙，民眾便已經彎身爬進店內搶購T恤，連門店鐵閘都疑被民眾撞彎；而貨架上KAWS的T恤亦被一掃而空，民眾不看呎碼，連模特兒公仔身上的都被脫出拿走。<br />\n<br />\n有網民表示，群情洶湧得如在看《屍殺列車》、「笑死，閘都彎埋」、「搶包山咁」；也有人指大部分都是黃牛黨，搶購T恤炒賣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1014584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1014584&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOBvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=7ab3a2f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1014584&h=cdd276a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1014584</a>"},{"pid":"fddff761e10672001d1008d30f75cd4880045f6f","tid":1183822,"uid":3138,"like":465,"dislike":2,"score":463,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:40:58.000Z","msg":"Uniqlo都有得炒？"},{"pid":"8ff7b055e3535d66e130a2b61535954e8fc249e3","tid":1183822,"uid":24044,"like":288,"dislike":4,"score":284,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:41:08.000Z","msg":"頭先落樓下個間買，大把貨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dff3cbbf767b4cbf6360628767eaa100ec3097d",